    "body": "Currently I don't believe this is possible with the built in Electron start at login API.\n\nMany apps use this tool.\n\n~~https://www.npmjs.com/package/node-autostart~~\nEDIT: https://github.com/Teamwork/node-auto-launch\n\nWhich allows you to pass custom arguments to the app when it launches, so you can pass `--auto-start` and read that in your app to automatically minimize itself when it launches.\n\nIn the future please ask question on the discussion forum or in slack.  GitHub is for bugs and issue reports\n"
