    "created_at": "2017-02-01T17:51:13Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-02-01T17:51:13Z",
    "body": "Thanks @MarshallOfSound for the pointer.\r\nBTW, I am using [https://www.npmjs.com/package/auto-launch](url)\r\n\r\nThe **isHidden: true** adds **--hidden** argument when it starts the application, you can do something like the following.\r\n\r\n> var startMinimized = (process.argv || []).indexOf('--hidden') !== -1;\r\n> \r\n> if (startMinimized == true){\r\n>       console.log('App is started by AutoLaunch');\r\n> }\r\n> else {\r\n>       console.log('App is started by User');\r\n> }\r\n"
  },
